        <h2>FIRING FEES AND MAKE-UP CLASSES</h2>
        <P>
                A fee of $.01 cents per cubic inch will charged to fire work, this fee includes both bisque and glaze firings.

                Students may make up missed classes at any other class time during the same session by emailing info@handmadepottery.com to inquire about available spaces.
                
               <p>+ $50 non-refundable deposit is required at registration.</p> 
                
                <p>+ <strong>No Refunds</strong> will be given once the session begins.</p>
                
                <p>+ Fees may not be transferred to another session.</p>
                
               <p>+ Class Fee includes one two hour class a week, all materials, tools and practice time during scheduled hours.</p> 
                
               
        </P>
</section>

